        "slowEndTime": 5583
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Writing the Perfect Cover Letter.\"",
        "startTime": 4259,
        "endTime": 5735,
        "slowStartTime": 6539,
        "slowEndTime": 8827
    },
    {
        "text": "There's a job you really want.",
        "startTime": 6717,
        "endTime": 8144,
        "slowStartTime": 10225,
        "slowEndTime": 12441
    },
    {
        "text": "Question is, how do you get one foot in the door?",
        "startTime": 8436,
        "endTime": 11235,
        "slowStartTime": 12804,
        "slowEndTime": 17078
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, the first step is to have an awesome cover letter.",
        "startTime": 11551,
        "endTime": 14722,
        "slowStartTime": 17477,
        "slowEndTime": 22308
    },
    {
        "text": "A cover letter is a great opportunity to tailor your qualifications to a job opening.",
        "startTime": 15133,
        "endTime": 19841,
        "slowStartTime": 22850,
        "slowEndTime": 29986
    },
    {
        "text": "Think of it as a summary of your resume.",
        "startTime": 20409,
        "endTime": 22859,
        "slowStartTime": 30764,
        "slowEndTime": 34514
    },
    {
        "text": "It's objective is to generate interest in a reviewer...",
        "startTime": 23207,
        "endTime": 25930,
        "slowStartTime": 34960,
        "slowEndTime": 39120
    },
    {
        "text": "...to look at your detailed resume and get an interview.",
        "startTime": 26313,
        "endTime": 28969,
        "slowStartTime": 39619,
        "slowEndTime": 43679
    },
    {
        "text": "Some HR professionals think a cover letter is not important,...",
        "startTime": 29618,
        "endTime": 33131,
        "slowStartTime": 44577,
        "slowEndTime": 49921
    },
    {
        "text": "...but we know it can give you an edge over others.",
        "startTime": 33379,
        "endTime": 35955,
        "slowStartTime": 50218,
        "slowEndTime": 54158
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, here are a few tips to help you prepare that perfect cover letter.",
        "startTime": 36759,
        "endTime": 40709,
        "slowStartTime": 55289,
        "slowEndTime": 61288
    },
    {
        "text": "Tip number 1: Address to the right person.",
        "startTime": 41295,
        "endTime": 44337,
        "slowStartTime": 62093,
        "slowEndTime": 66730
    },
    {
        "text": "Avoid general salutations such as, \"Dear HR Manager.\"",
        "startTime": 44942,
        "endTime": 48529,
        "slowStartTime": 67563,
        "slowEndTime": 73019
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't be cold.",
        "startTime": 49357,
        "endTime": 50327,
        "slowStartTime": 74186,
        "slowEndTime": 75715
    },
    {
        "text": "Be personal.",
        "startTime": 50512,
        "endTime": 51243,
        "slowStartTime": 75918,
        "slowEndTime": 77090
    },
    {
        "text": "Find out who is in charge and address your document to the right person.",
        "startTime": 51688,
        "endTime": 55188,
        "slowStartTime": 77682,
        "slowEndTime": 83007
    },
    {
        "text": "Tip number 2: Make your cover letter concise.",
        "startTime": 56209,
        "endTime": 58712,
        "slowStartTime": 84463,
        "slowEndTime": 88293
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't overwrite.",
        "startTime": 59609,
        "endTime": 60371,
        "slowStartTime": 89564,
        "slowEndTime": 90781
    },
    {
        "text": "Keep it to three paragraphs and have all your information within one A4 page.",
        "startTime": 60939,
        "endTime": 65009,
        "slowStartTime": 91558,
        "slowEndTime": 97739
    },
    {
        "text": "Start the letter by telling HR how you learned about the organization and the job opening.",
        "startTime": 66163,
        "endTime": 70899,
        "slowStartTime": 99395,
        "slowEndTime": 106573
    },
    {
        "text": "If the company is good, sing its praises.",
        "startTime": 71365,
        "endTime": 73480,
        "slowStartTime": 107197,
        "slowEndTime": 110445
    },
    {
        "text": "A little bootlicking goes a long way.",
        "startTime": 73874,
        "endTime": 75644,
        "slowStartTime": 110961,
        "slowEndTime": 113691
    },
    {
        "text": "In paragraph two, justify why you are perfect for the job...",
        "startTime": 77113,
        "endTime": 80278,
        "slowStartTime": 115819,
        "slowEndTime": 120642
    },
    {
        "text": "...and how you can contribute to the company.",
        "startTime": 80731,
        "endTime": 82349,
        "slowStartTime": 121247,
        "slowEndTime": 123748
    },
    {
        "text": "You should also include your education qualification and previous job accomplishments.",
        "startTime": 83488,
        "endTime": 87497,
        "slowStartTime": 125382,
        "slowEndTime": 131470
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember to quantify your accomplishments with evidence such as statistics and awards.",
        "startTime": 88400,
        "endTime": 93503,
        "slowStartTime": 132750,
        "slowEndTime": 140479
    },
    {
        "text": "The final paragraph is where you leave that positive, lasting impression...",
        "startTime": 95384,
        "endTime": 98869,
        "slowStartTime": 143226,
        "slowEndTime": 148529
    },
    {
        "text": "...by reaffirming your interest in the job.",
        "startTime": 99157,
        "endTime": 101015,
        "slowStartTime": 148885,
        "slowEndTime": 151748
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember to include your contact details, and most importantly,...",
        "startTime": 102354,
        "endTime": 105690,
        "slowStartTime": 153681,
        "slowEndTime": 158760
    },
    {
        "text": "...don't forget to thank the reviewer.",
        "startTime": 106065,
        "endTime": 107527,
        "slowStartTime": 159248,
        "slowEndTime": 161516
    },
    {
        "text": "Tip number 3: Never reuse your cover letter.",
        "startTime": 108729,
        "endTime": 111727,
        "slowStartTime": 163244,
        "slowEndTime": 167816
    },
    {
        "text": "Each job vacancy is unique.",
        "startTime": 112331,
        "endTime": 114059,
        "slowStartTime": 168646,
        "slowEndTime": 171314
    },
    {
        "text": "You should therefore customize your cover letter accordingly.",
        "startTime": 114850,
        "endTime": 117848,
        "slowStartTime": 172425,
        "slowEndTime": 176997
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't be lazy!",
        "startTime": 118270,
        "endTime": 119185,
        "slowStartTime": 177555,
        "slowEndTime": 179003
    },
    {
        "text": "So to summarize the ingredients of a good cover letter.",
        "startTime": 119711,
        "endTime": 122583,
        "slowStartTime": 179717,
        "slowEndTime": 184100
    },
    {
        "text": "Number 1: Address to the right person.",
        "startTime": 123007,
        "endTime": 125541,
        "slowStartTime": 184661,
        "slowEndTime": 188536
    },
    {
        "text": "Number 2: Keep it concise.",
        "startTime": 125875,
        "endTime": 127685,
        "slowStartTime": 188963,
        "slowEndTime": 191753
    },
    {
        "text": "And finally, number 3: Never reuse your cover letter.",
        "startTime": 128006,
        "endTime": 131747,
        "slowStartTime": 192159,
        "slowEndTime": 197846
    },
